(1704,	'Joc de Trons',	824,	'George R. R. Martin',	'unknown',	'2022-01-01 00:00:00',	'***A Game of Thrones*** is the inaugural novel in ***A Song of Ice and Fire***, an epic series of fantasy novels crafted by the American author **George R. R. Martin**. Published on August 1, 1996, this novel introduces readers to the richly detailed world of Westeros and Essos, where political intrigue, power struggles, and magical elements intertwine.

